Package: pkgbootstrap
Title: Bootstrap an Opinionated R Package Setup
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:c(
    person("Bjarke", "Hautop", , "bjarke.hautop@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
  )
Description: Creates a new R package with an opinionated setup: air
    formatting, git and GitHub, an Rmd
    README with badges, codecov test coverage, spell checking, GitHub
    Actions workflows, Dependabot, a pkgdown site on GitHub Pages, and
    pre-commit hooks installed with prek.
